{"tid":1836702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局：過去24小時新增35個疑似個案 暫時單日最高","createTime":"2020-01-23T09:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T12:01:27.000Z","uid":212626,"like":209,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"37225a9441956c63e90cd895763ab648334e231f","tid":1836702,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:56:09.000Z","msg":"醫管局公布截至中午12時，公立醫院在過去24小時，接收35名符合「嚴重新型傳染性病原體呼吸系統病」呈報準則的病人，當中包括12男23女、年齡由5個月至86歲，樣本將送交衞生署化驗。<br />\n<br />\n目前有55人正留院接受隔離，53人情況穩定，2名北區醫院病人因自身疾病情況危殆。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504448-20200123.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504448-20200123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=7a1f3d43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504448-20200123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d06376b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504448-20200123.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"362389dfadfa2089cb1c87fb3950f8d1fd6a9280","tid":1836702,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82dd14ee96098aff961f69ce633bc432f6bb9fc","tid":1836702,"uid":72185,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"你老尾 今日至第二日炸"},{"pid":"f6eb506bc4a013e3a74cf7cc0af21aeba5add741","tid":1836702,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b54d7fcd2c7240327991d5f785c2d08e2d5208","tid":1836702,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no